001package gbw.melange.common.builders;
002
003import gbw.melange.common.elementary.contraints.Anchor;
004import gbw.melange.common.elementary.contraints.ElementAnchoring;
005import gbw.melange.common.elementary.types.IConstrainedElement;
006
007/**
008 * <p>ISpaceBuilder interface.</p>
009 *
010 * @author GustavBW
011 * @version $Id: $Id
012 */
013public interface ISpaceBuilder extends IBuilder<IConstrainedElement>{
014    /**
015     * <p>setWidth.</p>
016     *
017     * @param percentSPX SPX = screen space x-axis / width.
018     * @return a {@link gbw.melange.common.builders.ISpaceBuilder} object
019     */
020    ISpaceBuilder setWidth(double percentSPX);
021
022    /**
023     * <p>setHeight.</p>
024     *
025     * @param percentSPY SPX = screen space y-axis / height.
026     * @return a {@link gbw.melange.common.builders.ISpaceBuilder} object
027     */
028    ISpaceBuilder setHeight(double percentSPY);
029    /**
030     * <p>setSelfAnchor.</p>
031     *
032     * @param anchor a {@link gbw.melange.common.elementary.contraints.ElementAnchoring} object
033     * @return a {@link gbw.melange.common.builders.ISpaceBuilder} object
034     */
035    ISpaceBuilder setSelfAnchor(ElementAnchoring anchor);
036    /**
037     * <p>setSelfAnchor.</p>
038     *
039     * @param anchor a {@link gbw.melange.common.elementary.contraints.Anchor} object
040     * @return a {@link gbw.melange.common.builders.ISpaceBuilder} object
041     */
042    ISpaceBuilder setSelfAnchor(Anchor anchor);
043    /**
044     * <p>setAttachingAnchor.</p>
045     *
046     * @param anchor a {@link gbw.melange.common.elementary.contraints.ElementAnchoring} object
047     * @return a {@link gbw.melange.common.builders.ISpaceBuilder} object
048     */
049    ISpaceBuilder setAttachingAnchor(ElementAnchoring anchor);
050    /**
051     * <p>setAttachingAnchor.</p>
052     *
053     * @param anchor a {@link gbw.melange.common.elementary.contraints.Anchor} object
054     * @return a {@link gbw.melange.common.builders.ISpaceBuilder} object
055     */
056    ISpaceBuilder setAttachingAnchor(Anchor anchor);
057}
